# 💼 Personal Portfolio Website

## 📌 Project Overview

The **Personal Portfolio Website** is a web-based project developed using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.
This project showcases my skills, projects, and personal information in a structured and visually appealing format.

The main purpose of this portfolio is to create an **online presence** and present my work effectively to recruiters and interviewers.

---

## 🚀 Features

* 👤 About Me section
* 🛠️ Skills display
* 📂 Projects showcase
* 📞 Contact section
* 🌐 Responsive design (works on mobile and desktop)
* 🎨 Attractive UI with simple navigation

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* **HTML** – Structure of the website
* **CSS** – Styling and layout design
* **JavaScript** – Interactivity and dynamic elements

